          <p>With components and wires clearly visible, installations are created that are meant to evoke amazement at the usually hidden complexity
            of technology.</p>
          <p>Older electromechanical parts, whose operation is clearly visible and understandable, are considered especially beautiful.</p>
          <p>By combining these with modern components, such as LEDs, micro-controllers and semiconductors, together with moving parts, such as marble
            tracks and electric motors, interesting objects are created.</p>

